data.description: Just Reduced, Don't miss out on this Newly Renovated 4 bedroom, 2 bathroom, with new deck and three bonus rooms.   This home has been remodeled through an open concept first floor with large spacious rooms throughout, two large bedrooms on the first floor and a large walk in closet off of the master bathroom.  The kitchen has  granite has counter tops, and all new kitchen appliances and a breakfast bar to seat a crowd.  Second floor has three bonus rooms, two sun rooms and an office or nursery and two additional bedrooms.  This home has a full basement  and large backyard.  Motivated seller, so get your favorite Realtor and schedule an appointment today!   Buyers and Buyer agents to verify all information on the property.   Seller to provide a passing city occupancy inspection.    Did I say motivated seller, make offer!   OPEN HOUSES,  Saturday and Sunday
